(1, 1, 'Skill Rating', '<p>The best yardstick for our progress is not other people, but ourselves. Am I better than I was yesterday? This is the only question worth asking. As long as you go to bed at night a better practitioner than the one who woke up that morning, you have succeeded. Your worth should have nothing to do with how your progress stacks up relative to another.</p>', '95', '90', '88', '60', '65', '75', '85', '65', '60', '80', '75', '2021-05-06 17:51:02', '2021-05-07 00:50:17', NULL);

