(1, 1, 1, 'The summary of education & qualifications', '<p>An education summary is the section of my resume where I highlight my academic qualifications and achievements. ... The education summary section usually comes after my work experience if I have an employment history. An education summary should include only relevant academic qualifications and accomplishments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://sohelarman.info//storage/photos/1/skill.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20160817/c1_1063796_160817134155.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>', '2021-05-07 22:36:52', '2021-05-09 21:19:57');

